        <dev:code>PS C:\&gt; (Get-DateTimeOffset -DateTime '2020-08-25T12:00:00' -Latitude 38.71667 -Longitude -9.13333 -Method TimeApi -Uri 'https://www.timeapi.io').ToString('o')
25/08/2020 12:00:00 +01:00</dev:code>
        <dev:remarks>
          <maml:para>This example uses the Time API. The -Method and -Uri parameters are optional and this example shows the default values.</maml:para>
